{"sha": "f48af912ea9a9726ff851a3e4a809e1d2daeb0ba", "node_id": "C_kwDOAAsO6NoAKGY0OGFmOTEyZWE5YTk3MjZmZjg1MWEzZTRhODA5ZTFkMmRhZWIwYmE", "commit": {"author": {"name": "bors", "email": "bors@rust-lang.org", "date": "2022-08-28T01:34:47Z"}, "committer": {"name": "bors", "email": "bors@rust-lang.org", "date": "2022-08-28T01:34:47Z"}, "message": "Auto merge of #96946 - WaffleLapkin:ptr_mask, r=scottmcm\n\nAdd pointer masking convenience functions\n\nThis PR adds the following public API:\n```rust\nimpl<T: ?Sized> *const T {\n    fn mask(self, mask: usize) -> *const T;\n}\n\nimpl<T: ?Sized> *mut T {\n    fn mask(self, mask: usize) -> *const T;\n}\n\n// mod intrinsics\nfn mask<T>(ptr: *const T, mask: usize) -> *const T\n```\nThis is equivalent to `ptr.map_addr(|a| a & mask)` but also uses a cool llvm intrinsic.\n\nProposed in https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/95643#issuecomment-1121562352\n\ncc `@Gankra` `@scottmcm` `@RalfJung`\n\nr? rust-lang/libs-api", "tree": {"sha": "554e0315662fce79d79de33fc05cb3def7d3392a", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/554e0315662fce79d79de33fc05cb3def7d3392a"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/f48af912ea9a9726ff851a3e4a809e1d2daeb0ba", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/f48af912ea9a9726ff851a3e4a809e1d2daeb0ba", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/f48af912ea9a9726ff851a3e4a809e1d2daeb0ba", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/f48af912ea9a9726ff851a3e4a809e1d2daeb0ba/comments", "author": {"login": "bors", "id": 3372342, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzNzIzNDI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3372342?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors", "html_url": "https://github.com/bors", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/followers", "following